6	 *
7	 * Train Recorder is a React Native / Expo app with client-side SQLite.
8	 * There is no HTTP API server. The "API" test cases verify service-layer
9	 * functions (progressive-overload, timer, stats) that run in the app's
10	 * JavaScript runtime.
11	 *
12	 * These tests exercise service logic via the app's web interface or
13	 * through programmatic invocation during E2E sessions.
